<plot>It is Christmas Eve and Claire is on her way home to spend the holiday with her family when she picks up a hitchhiker, Caleb. As the trip progresses, the two start talking. Caleb tells Claire about the horrifying Christmas party that he attended earlier that night. A Christmas party in which he was bitten by a werewolf. As the conversation continues, Caleb tries to resist his urge to give in to his new craving.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?550766</url></doc>
